You are being asked to participate in a student class project. This project is being conducted by the students of Marquette University COSC 4500 Advanced Data Science.

Participating in this project is completely voluntary. You may stop participating at any time. There are no direct benefits to you for participating but results from this study will provide information that may benefit the general population.

Any information collected for this project will only be used for class purposes. No information will be published, presented at conferences, or otherwise shared publicly. This project has not been approved by the Marquette University Institutional Review Board.



If you have any questions about this project please contact Liam Fruzyna at liam.fruzyna@marquette.edu, Reid Holben at reid.holben@marquette.edu, or Vidit Kalani at vidit.kalani@marquette.edu.
